{\s17\sa60\sb30\widctlpar\qj \fs22\cgrid 
Removes a book from both the local list and the user interface.\par
Iterates through the local book list to find and remove the specified book. Updates the UI by removing the corresponding visual representation of the book. If the book is marked as being in the database, attempts to remove it from there as well. Handles exceptions that may occur during database operations and provides user feedback.\par
